WITH
    CTE AS
    (
        SELECT
            BFLC12.*,
            CASE
                WHEN tipo='CONVENIO'
                THEN cagrseg_new
                ELSE contratante_rut
            END AS num_convenio
        FROM
            (
                SELECT
                    BFLC.*,
                    FIN_VIG_ORIG - INI_VIG AS Dias_Vigencia,
                    CURRENT_DATE-INI_VIG   AS dias_transcurridos_1,
                    CASE
                        WHEN BFLC.cagrseg IS NULL
                        THEN
                            CASE
                                WHEN (MX_B.MX_CAGRSEG IS NOT NULL
                                    AND MX_B.MX_CAGRSEG NOT IN
                                        (
                                            SELECT
                                                CAST(num_convenio AS VARCHAR(8)) AS num_convenio
                                            FROM
                                                cdp_stg_dwh.convenios_excluidos))
                                THEN MX_B.MX_CAGRSEG
                            END
                        WHEN BFLC.cagrseg <> 0
                        OR  BFLC.cagrseg IS NOT NULL
                        THEN
                            CASE
                                WHEN (BFLC.cagrseg NOT IN
                                        (
                                            SELECT
                                                CAST(num_convenio AS VARCHAR(8)) AS num_convenio
                                            FROM
                                                cdp_stg_dwh.convenios_excluidos))
                                THEN BFLC.cagrseg
                                ELSE BFLC.cagrseg
                            END
                        ELSE BFLC.contratante_rut
                    END AS cagrseg_new,
                    CASE
                        WHEN BFLC.cagrseg IS NULL
                        THEN
                            CASE
                                WHEN (MX_B.MX_CAGRSEG IS NOT NULL
                                    AND MX_B.MX_CAGRSEG NOT IN
                                        (
                                            SELECT
                                                CAST(num_convenio AS VARCHAR(8)) AS num_convenio
                                            FROM
                                                cdp_stg_dwh.convenios_excluidos))
                                THEN 'CONVENIO'
                                ELSE 'NA'
                            END
                        WHEN BFLC.cagrseg <> 0
                        OR  BFLC.cagrseg IS NOT NULL
                        THEN
                            CASE
                                WHEN (BFLC.cagrseg NOT IN
                                        (
                                            SELECT
                                                CAST(num_convenio AS VARCHAR(8)) AS num_convenio
                                            FROM
                                                cdp_stg_dwh.convenios_excluidos))
                                THEN 'CONVENIO'
                                ELSE 'NA'
                            END
                    END AS tipo,
                    -------------------------------------------------
                    CASE
                        WHEN seg.cmonseg <> 'CLF'
                        THEN CAST((BFLC.prima * cct.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val)AS DECIMAL(25,10))
                        ELSE BFLC.prima
                    END AS premium_amount
                    --------------------------------------------------
                FROM
                    (
                        SELECT
                            *
                        FROM
                            CDP_DWH.base_final_liberty ) BFLC
                LEFT JOIN
                    (
                        SELECT
                            TA.NNUMNIF,
                            B.CAGENTE,
                            MAX(b.cagrseg) AS MX_CAGRSEG
                        FROM
                            CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_SEGUROS B,
                            CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_AGENTES A,
                            CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_PERSONAS CA,
                            CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_TOMADORES T,
                            CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_PERSONAS TA
                        WHERE
                            A.CAGENTE = B.CAGENTE
                        AND A.SPERSON = CA.SPERSON
                        AND T.SPERSON = TA.SPERSON
                        AND B.SSEGURO = T.SSEGURO
                        AND B.cagrseg IS NOT NULL
                        AND B.cagrseg NOT IN ('    ',
                                              '3000',
                                              '5482',
                                              '5483',
                                              '5500',
                                              '5491',
                                              '5488',
                                              '5504',
                                              '5486',
                                              '5496',
                                              '5502',
                                              '5485',
                                              '5490',
                                              '5487',
                                              '5493',
                                              '5498',
                                              '5516',
                                              '5494',
                                              '5489',
                                              '5503',
                                              '5524',
                                              '5495',
                                              '5497',
                                              '5501',
                                              '5547',
                                              '5659')
                        GROUP BY
                            TA.NNUMNIF ,
                            B.CAGENTE ) MX_B
                ON
                    BFLC.CONTRATANTE_RUT = SUBSTRING(MX_B.NNUMNIF,1,LEN(MX_B.NNUMNIF)-1)
                AND BFLC.CAGENTE = MX_B.CAGENTE
                    --where sseguro = 4384217
                    -------------------------------------------------------------------------
                LEFT JOIN
                    (
                        SELECT
                            sseguro,
                            cmonseg
                        FROM
                            cdp_ods.sisaxis_seguros ) seg
                ON
                    BFLC.sseguro = seg.sseguro
                LEFT JOIN
                    cdp_dwh.curr_conv_t cct
                ON
                    seg.cmonseg = cct.curr_cd --tipo de cambio
                AND CAST ((extract(YEAR FROM BFLC.fin_vig_act) || LPAD(extract(MONTH FROM
                    BFLC.fin_vig_act),2,0)) AS INTEGER) = CAST(substring(REPLACE(DATE(cct.vltn_dtm)
                    ,'-',''),1,6) AS INTEGER)
                    --and extract(MONTH from fin_vig_act) = to_char(vltn_dtm,'MM') --mes contable
                    --and s.acct_yr = to_char(vltn_dtm,'YYYY') --aÃ±o contable
                AND cct.src_sys_cd = 'axis' --sistema de origen
                AND cct.curr_conv_frequency_cd = 'Monthly' --frecuencia de cambio
            )BFLC12
    )
SELECT
    tipo_new,
    sseguro,
    poliza,
    item AS certificado,
    poliza_certificado,
    estado_actual,
    producto,
    actividad,
    deducible,
    num_convenio,
    cagente AS codigo_corredor,
    canal,
    substring(cagente, 1, (LEN(cagente) - 3)) AS cod_corredor,
    id_sucursal                               AS cod_sucursal,
    NVL(CD_CFLOTA, 0)                         AS CD_CFLOTA , --cflota,
    corredor                                  AS nombre_corredor,
    asegurado_rut                             AS rut_asegurado,
    contratante_rut                           AS rut_contratante,
    contratante_nombre                        AS contratante,
    ini_vig                                   AS fecha_inicio_vigencia,
    fin_vig_act                               AS fecha_termino_vigencia_actual,
    ano_mes_fin_vigencia_actual,
    fin_vig_orig AS fecha_termino_vigencia_original,
    ano_mes_inicio_vigencia,
    ano_fin_termino_original,
    ano_mes_fin_termino_original,
    dias_vigencia,
    dias_transcurridos,
    veh_tipo AS tipo_vehiculo,
    marca_vehiculo,
    modelo_vehiculo,
    patente   AS patente_vehiculo,
    num_motor AS numero_motor,
    veh_ano   AS ano_vehiculo,
    uso       AS uso_vehiculo,
    CASE
        WHEN premium_amount IS NULL
        THEN 0
        ELSE premium_amount ::DECIMAL(25,10)
    END AS prima_neta,
    CASE
        WHEN prima_anualizada IS NULL
        THEN 0
        ELSE prima_anualizada ::DECIMAL(25,10)
    END AS prima_anualizada,
    CASE
        WHEN prima_ganada IS NULL
        THEN 0
        ELSE prima_ganada ::DECIMAL(25,10)
    END AS prima_ganada,
    contador_siniestros,
    CASE
        WHEN pago_mo_new IS NULL
        THEN 0
        ELSE pago_mo_new
    END AS pagos_clf,
    CASE
        WHEN recup_mo_new IS NULL
        THEN 0
        ELSE recup_mo_new
    END AS recup_clf,
    CASE
        WHEN provision_mo_new IS NULL
        THEN 0
        ELSE provision_mo_new
    END AS provision_clf,
    porcentaje_comision,
    monto_comision_clf,
    'CLF' AS Moneda_Seguro,
    rec_crt_dtm,
    rec_updt_dtm,
    etl_audit_id,
    CASE
        WHEN tipo_new = 'CONVENIO'
        THEN ref_desc
        WHEN tipo_new = 'CONTRATANTE'
        THEN contratante_nombre
    END AS nombre,
    sucursal_suscripcion,
    asegurado
FROM
    (
        SELECT
            BFLC13.*,
            MODVEH.ref_desc AS modelo_vehiculo
        FROM
            (
                SELECT
                    BFLC12.*,
                    MARVEH.ref_desc AS marca_vehiculo
                FROM
                    (
                        SELECT
                            BFLC11.*,
                            PER.tbuscar AS asegurado
                        FROM
                            (
                                SELECT
                                    BFLC10.* ,
                                    BROFF.branch_office_name AS sucursal_suscripcion
                                FROM
                                    (
                                        SELECT
                                            BFLC9.*,
                                            ref_cd,
                                            ref_desc
                                        FROM
                                            (
                                                SELECT
                                                    BFLC8.*,
                                                    CASE
                                                        WHEN PRMO.provision_mo IS NULL
                                                        THEN NULL
                                                        WHEN PRMO.id_moneda <> 'CLF'
                                                        THEN CAST((PRMO.provision_mo *
                                                            cct3.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val) AS DECIMAL
                                                            (25,10))
                                                        ELSE PRMO.provision_mo
                                                    END AS provision_mo_new,
                                                    CAST ((extract(YEAR FROM ini_vig) || LPAD
                                                    (extract(MONTH FROM ini_vig),2,0)) AS INTEGER)
                                                    AS ano_mes_inicio_vigencia,
                                                    CAST ((extract(YEAR FROM fin_vig_act) || LPAD
                                                    (extract(MONTH FROM fin_vig_act),2,0)) AS
                                                    INTEGER) AS ano_mes_fin_vigencia_actual,
                                                    CASE
                                                        WHEN csituac=0
                                                        THEN 'Vigente'
                                                        WHEN csituac=2
                                                        THEN 'Anulado/Cancelado'
                                                        WHEN csituac=5
                                                        THEN 'Endoso Pendiente'
                                                    END               AS estado_actual,
                                                    poliza||'-'||item AS poliza_certificado,
                                                    CAST (extract(YEAR FROM FIN_VIG_ORIG) AS
                                                    INTEGER) AS Ano_Fin_Termino_Original,
                                                    CAST ((extract(YEAR FROM FIN_VIG_ORIG) || LPAD
                                                    (extract(MONTH FROM FIN_VIG_ORIG),2,0)) AS
                                                    INTEGER) AS Ano_Mes_Fin_Termino_Original
                                                FROM
                                                    (
                                                        SELECT
                                                            BFLC7.*,
                                                            ----------------------------------------------------------
                                                            CASE
                                                                WHEN REMO.recup_mo IS NULL
                                                                THEN NULL
                                                                WHEN REMO.id_moneda <> 'CLF'
                                                                THEN CAST((REMO.recup_mo *
                                                                    cct2.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val) AS
                                                                    DECIMAL(25,10))
                                                                ELSE REMO.recup_mo
                                                            END AS recup_mo_new
                                                            --REMO.recup_mo
                                                            ----------------------------------------------------------
                                                        FROM
                                                            (
                                                                SELECT
                                                                    BFLC6.* ,
                                                                    -----------------------------
                                                                    CASE
                                                                        WHEN PAMO.pago_mo IS NULL
                                                                        THEN NULL
                                                                        WHEN PAMO.id_moneda <>
                                                                            'CLF'
                                                                        THEN CAST((PAMO.pago_mo *
                                                                            cct1.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val
                                                                            )AS DECIMAL(25,10))
                                                                        ELSE PAMO.pago_mo
                                                                    END AS pago_mo_new
                                                                    --PAMO.pago_mo
                                                                    -----------------------------
                                                                FROM
                                                                    (
                                                                        SELECT
                                                                            BFLC5.*,
                                                                            SIN.Contador_Siniestros
                                                                        FROM
                                                                            (
                                                                                SELECT
                                                                                    BFLC4.*,
                                                                                    CASE
                                                                                        WHEN
                                                                                            CD_CFLOTA
                                                                                            =1
                                                                                        THEN
                                                                                            'Flota'
                                                                                        ELSE
                                                                                            'Individual'
                                                                                    END AS canal,
                                                                                    (COMSEG.PCOMISI
                                                                                    )::DECIMAL(25,
                                                                                    10) AS
                                                                                    Porcentaje_Comision
                                                                                    ,
                                                                                    (premium_amount
                                                                                    *
                                                                                    COMSEG.PCOMISI
                                                                                    / 100) ::
                                                                                    DECIMAL(25,10)
                                                                                    AS
                                                                                    Monto_Comision_CLF
                                                                                    ,
                                                                                    CASE
                                                                                        WHEN
                                                                                            dias_transcurridos
                                                                                            >=
                                                                                            dias_vigencia
                                                                                        THEN
                                                                                            (
                                                                                            premium_amount
                                                                                            ) ::
                                                                                            DECIMAL
                                                                                            (25,10)
                                                                                        ELSE
                                                                                            (
                                                                                            premium_amount
                                                                                            /NULLIF
                                                                                            (
                                                                                            dias_vigencia
                                                                                            *
                                                                                            dias_transcurridos
                                                                                            ,0)) ::
                                                                                            DECIMAL
                                                                                            (25,10)
                                                                                    END AS
                                                                                    prima_ganada
                                                                                FROM
                                                                                    (
                                                                                        SELECT
                                                                                            BFLC3.*
                                                                                            ,
                                                                                            CD.CFLOTA
                                                                                            AS
                                                                                            CD_CFLOTA
                                                                                        FROM
                                                                                            (
                                                                                                SELECT
                                                                                                    BFLC2.*
                                                                                                    ,
                                                                                                    ACTI.TACTIVI
                                                                                                    AS
                                                                                                    Actividad
                                                                                                FROM
                                                                                                    (
                                                                                                        SELECT
                                                                                                            *
                                                                                                        FROM
                                                                                                            (
                                                                                                                SELECT
                                                                                                                    CTE.*
                                                                                                                    ,
                                                                                                                    CTE1.count_sseguro
                                                                                                                    ,
                                                                                                                    CASE
                                                                                                                        WHEN
                                                                                                                            tipo
                                                                                                                            =
                                                                                                                            'CONVENIO'
                                                                                                                        THEN
                                                                                                                            tipo
                                                                                                                        WHEN
                                                                                                                            (
                                                                                                                                num_convenio
                                                                                                                                IS NOT NULL
                                                                                                                            AND
                                                                                                                                count_sseguro
                                                                                                                                >
                                                                                                                                4
                                                                                                                            AND
                                                                                                                                tipo
                                                                                                                                =
                                                                                                                                'NA'
                                                                                                                            )
                                                                                                                        THEN
                                                                                                                            'CONTRATANTE'
                                                                                                                            --
                                                                                                                            -- tipo
                                                                                                                            -- is
                                                                                                                            -- null
                                                                                                                        ELSE
                                                                                                                            'NA'
                                                                                                                    END
                                                                                                                    AS
                                                                                                                    tipo_new
                                                                                                                    ,
                                                                                                                    CASE
                                                                                                                        WHEN
                                                                                                                            (
                                                                                                                                DIAS_VIGENCIA
                                                                                                                                =
                                                                                                                                0
                                                                                                                            OR
                                                                                                                                premium_amount
                                                                                                                                =
                                                                                                                                0
                                                                                                                            )
                                                                                                                        THEN
                                                                                                                            0
                                                                                                                        WHEN
                                                                                                                            DIAS_VIGENCIA
                                                                                                                            <>
                                                                                                                            0
                                                                                                                        THEN
                                                                                                                            (
                                                                                                                            (
                                                                                                                            premium_amount
                                                                                                                            /
                                                                                                                            DIAS_VIGENCIA
                                                                                                                            )
                                                                                                                            *
                                                                                                                            365
                                                                                                                            )
                                                                                                                            ::
                                                                                                                            DECIMAL
                                                                                                                            (
                                                                                                                            25
                                                                                                                            ,
                                                                                                                            10
                                                                                                                            )
                                                                                                                    END
                                                                                                                    AS
                                                                                                                    Prima_Anualizada
                                                                                                                    ,
                                                                                                                    CASE
                                                                                                                        WHEN
                                                                                                                            dias_transcurridos_1
                                                                                                                            >
                                                                                                                            dias_vigencia
                                                                                                                        THEN
                                                                                                                            dias_vigencia
                                                                                                                        ELSE
                                                                                                                            dias_transcurridos_1
                                                                                                                    END
                                                                                                                    AS
                                                                                                                    dias_transcurridos
                                                                                                                FROM
                                                                                                                    CTE
                                                                                                                    --
                                                                                                                    -- as
                                                                                                                    -- CTE_ref
                                                                                                                LEFT JOIN
                                                                                                                    (
                                                                                                                        SELECT
                                                                                                                            contratante_rut
                                                                                                                            ,
                                                                                                                            COUNT
                                                                                                                            (
                                                                                                                            sseguro
                                                                                                                            )
                                                                                                                            AS
                                                                                                                            count_sseguro
                                                                                                                        FROM
                                                                                                                            CTE
                                                                                                                        WHERE
                                                                                                                            cagrseg
                                                                                                                            =
                                                                                                                            0
                                                                                                                        OR
                                                                                                                            cagrseg
                                                                                                                            IS NULL
                                                                                                                            --
                                                                                                                            -- num_convenio
                                                                                                                            -- ,
                                                                                                                            -- cagrseg
                                                                                                                        GROUP BY
                                                                                                                            contratante_rut
                                                                                                                    )
                                                                                                                    CTE1
                                                                                                                ON
                                                                                                                    CTE.contratante_rut
                                                                                                                    =
                                                                                                                    CTE1.contratante_rut
                                                                                                            )
                                                                                                        WHERE
                                                                                                            tipo_new
                                                                                                            <>
                                                                                                            'NA'
                                                                                                    )
                                                                                                    BFLC2
                                                                                                LEFT JOIN
                                                                                                    (
                                                                                                        SELECT DISTINCT
                                                                                                            S.SSEGURO
                                                                                                            ,
                                                                                                            A.TACTIVI
                                                                                                        FROM
                                                                                                            CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_SEGUROS
                                                                                                            S
                                                                                                            ,
                                                                                                            CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_ACTIVISEGU
                                                                                                            A
                                                                                                        WHERE
                                                                                                            S.CACTIVI
                                                                                                            =
                                                                                                            A.CACTIVI
                                                                                                        AND
                                                                                                            A.CRAMO
                                                                                                            =
                                                                                                            6
                                                                                                        AND
                                                                                                            A.CIDIOMA
                                                                                                            =
                                                                                                            3
                                                                                                    )
                                                                                                    ACTI
                                                                                                ON
                                                                                                    BFLC2.SSEGURO
                                                                                                    =
                                                                                                    ACTI.SSEGURO
                                                                                            ) BFLC3
                                                                                        LEFT JOIN
                                                                                            CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_CTR_DESAGRUPASEG
                                                                                            CD
                                                                                        ON
                                                                                            BFLC3.CAGRSEG
                                                                                            =
                                                                                            CD.CAGRSEG
                                                                                    ) BFLC4
                                                                                LEFT JOIN
                                                                                    (
                                                                                        SELECT DISTINCT
                                                                                            SSEGURO
                                                                                            ,
                                                                                            PCOMISI
                                                                                        FROM
                                                                                            cdp_ods.sisaxis_comisionsegu
                                                                                        WHERE
                                                                                            nmovimi
                                                                                            = 1)
                                                                                    COMSEG
                                                                                ON
                                                                                    BFLC4.SSEGURO =
                                                                                    COMSEG.SSEGURO
                                                                            ) BFLC5
                                                                        LEFT JOIN
                                                                            (
                                                                                SELECT
                                                                                    sseguro,
                                                                                    COUNT (DISTINCT
                                                                                    nsinies) AS
                                                                                    Contador_Siniestros
                                                                                FROM
                                                                                    cdp_ods.sisaxis_SINIESTROS
                                                                                GROUP BY
                                                                                    sseguro) SIN
                                                                        ON
                                                                            BFLC5.SSEGURO =
                                                                            SIN.SSEGURO ) BFLC6
                                                                LEFT JOIN
                                                                    (
                                                                        SELECT
                                                                            sin.cie_sseguro AS
                                                                            id_item,
                                                                            seg.cmonseg AS
                                                                            id_moneda,
                                                                            SUM(sin.cie_mto_mo) AS
                                                                            pago_mo
                                                                        FROM
                                                                            cdp_ods.siscierres_sin_ciemen_tbl
                                                                            sin,
                                                                            cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SEGUROS
                                                                            seg
                                                                        WHERE
                                                                            cie_est_proceso=1
                                                                        AND cie_tip_pro = 1
                                                                        AND cie_sseguro =
                                                                            seg.sseguro
                                                                        GROUP BY
                                                                            cie_sseguro,
                                                                            seg.cmonseg ) PAMO
                                                                ON
                                                                    BFLC6.sseguro = PAMO.id_item
                                                                    -------------------------
                                                                LEFT JOIN
                                                                    cdp_dwh.curr_conv_t cct1
                                                                ON
                                                                    PAMO.id_moneda = cct1.curr_cd
                                                                    --tipo de cambio
                                                                AND CAST ((extract(YEAR FROM
                                                                    fin_vig_act) || LPAD(extract
                                                                    (MONTH FROM fin_vig_act),2,0))
                                                                    AS INTEGER) = CAST(substring
                                                                    (REPLACE(DATE(cct1.vltn_dtm),
                                                                    '-',''),1,6) AS INTEGER)
                                                                    --and extract(MONTH from
                                                                    -- fin_vig_act) = to_char
                                                                    -- (vltn_dtm,'MM') --mes
                                                                    -- contable
                                                                    --and s.acct_yr = to_char
                                                                    -- (vltn_dtm,'YYYY') --aÃ±o
                                                                    -- contable
                                                                AND cct1.src_sys_cd = 'axis' --
                                                                    -- sistema de origen
                                                                AND cct1.curr_conv_frequency_cd =
                                                                    'Monthly'
                                                                    -------------------------
                                                            ) BFLC7
                                                        LEFT JOIN
                                                            (
                                                                SELECT
                                                                    sin.cie_sseguro     AS id_item,
                                                                    seg.cmonseg        AS id_moneda,
                                                                    SUM(sin.cie_mto_mo) AS recup_mo
                                                                FROM
                                                                    CDP_ODS.siscierres_sin_ciemen_tbl
                                                                    sin,
                                                                    CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_SEGUROS seg
                                                                WHERE
                                                                    cie_est_proceso=1
                                                                AND cie_tip_pro = 2
                                                                AND cie_sseguro = seg.sseguro
                                                                GROUP BY
                                                                    cie_sseguro,
                                                                    seg.cmonseg )REMO
                                                        ON
                                                            BFLC7.SSEGURO = REMO.id_item
                                                            -----------------------------------------------------
                                                        LEFT JOIN
                                                            cdp_dwh.curr_conv_t cct2
                                                        ON
                                                            REMO.id_moneda = cct2.curr_cd --tipo de
                                                            -- cambio
                                                        AND CAST ((extract(YEAR FROM fin_vig_act)
                                                            || LPAD(extract(MONTH FROM fin_vig_act)
                                                            ,2,0)) AS INTEGER) = CAST(substring
                                                            (REPLACE(DATE(cct2.vltn_dtm),'-',''),1,
                                                            6) AS INTEGER)
                                                            --and extract(MONTH from fin_vig_act) =
                                                            -- to_char(vltn_dtm,'MM') --mes
                                                            -- contable
                                                            --and s.acct_yr = to_char(vltn_dtm,'
                                                            -- YYYY') --aÃ±o contable
                                                        AND cct2.src_sys_cd = 'axis' --sistema de
                                                            -- origen
                                                        AND cct2.curr_conv_frequency_cd = 'Monthly'
                                                            -----------------------------------------------------
                                                    ) BFLC8
                                                LEFT JOIN
                                                    (
                                                        SELECT
                                                            sin.cie_sseguro AS id_item,
                                                            seg.cmonseg     AS id_moneda,
                                                            sin.cie_per_con,
                                                            SUM(sin.cie_mto_mo) AS provision_mo
                                                        FROM
                                                            cdp_ods.siscierres_sin_ciemen_tbl sin,
                                                            cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SEGUROS seg
                                                        WHERE
                                                            sin.cie_est_proceso=1
                                                        AND sin.cie_tip_pro = 3
                                                        AND sin.cie_sseguro = seg.sseguro
                                                        AND sin.cie_per_con =
                                                            (
                                                                SELECT
                                                                    MAX (cie_per_con)
                                                                FROM
                                                                    cdp_ods.siscierres_sin_ciemen_tbl
                                                                WHERE
                                                                    cie_est_proceso=1
                                                                AND cie_tip_pro = 3
                                                                AND cie_sseguro= sin.cie_sseguro
                                                                GROUP BY
                                                                    cie_sseguro)
                                                        GROUP BY
                                                            sin.cie_sseguro,
                                                            seg.cmonseg,
                                                            sin.cie_per_con ) PRMO
                                                ON
                                                    BFLC8.sseguro = PRMO.id_item
                                                    ---------------------------------------------------------
                                                LEFT JOIN
                                                    cdp_dwh.curr_conv_t cct3
                                                ON
                                                    PRMO.id_moneda = cct3.curr_cd --tipo de cambio
                                                AND CAST ((extract(YEAR FROM fin_vig_act) || LPAD
                                                    (extract(MONTH FROM fin_vig_act),2,0)) AS
                                                    INTEGER) = CAST(substring(REPLACE(DATE
                                                    (cct3.vltn_dtm),'-',''),1,6) AS INTEGER)
                                                    --and extract(MONTH from fin_vig_act) = to_char
                                                    -- (vltn_dtm,'MM') --mes contable
                                                    --and s.acct_yr = to_char(vltn_dtm,'YYYY') --
                                                    -- aÃ±o contable
                                                AND cct3.src_sys_cd = 'axis' --sistema de origen
                                                AND cct3.curr_conv_frequency_cd = 'Monthly'
                                                    ---------------------------------------------------------
                                            ) BFLC9
                                        LEFT JOIN
                                            (
                                                SELECT
                                                    ref_cd,
                                                    ref_desc
                                                FROM
                                                    (
                                                        SELECT
                                                            ref_desc,
                                                            ref_cd,
                                                            row_number() over (partition BY ref_cd)
                                                            AS rnk
                                                        FROM
                                                            cdp_stg_dwh.stg_tref_code_map_variant
                                                        WHERE
                                                            ref_type_cd = 'agreement'
                                                        AND src_sys_cd = 'axis')
                                                WHERE
                                                    rnk=1 ) REFER
                                        ON
                                            BFLC9.num_convenio = REFER.ref_cd --BFLC9.cagrseg =
                                            -- REFER.ref_cd
                                    ) BFLC10
                                LEFT JOIN
                                    cdp_dwh.dim_branch_office_t BROFF
                                ON
                                    BFLC10.id_sucursal = BROFF.branch_office_cd
                                AND BROFF.SRC_SYS_CD='axis') BFLC11
                        LEFT JOIN
                            adp_dwh.cdp_ods.sisaxis_personas PER
                        ON
                            BFLC11.SPERSON = PER.SPERSON ) BFLC12
                LEFT JOIN
                    (
                        SELECT
                            ref_cd,
                            ref_desc
                        FROM
                            cdp_stg_dwh.stg_tref_code_map_variant
                        WHERE
                            ref_type_cd = 'veh_make'
                        AND src_sys_cd = 'axis' ) MARVEH
                ON
                    BFLC12.VEH_CMARCA = MARVEH.REF_CD ) BFLC13
        LEFT JOIN
            (
                SELECT
                    ref_cd,
                    ref_desc
                FROM
                    cdp_stg_dwh.stg_tref_code_map_variant
                WHERE
                    ref_type_cd = 'veh_model'
                AND src_sys_cd = 'axis' ) MODVEH
        ON
            (
                BFLC13.VEH_CMARCA||'|'||BFLC13.VEH_CMODELO) = MODVEH.ref_cd )
